	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings , <br><br>I'm Dytren Lang, Cleric of Tunare , and Member of Sacrosanct Legion , on the Rathe Server. <br><br>This journal is for the posting of Clerical Grouping Strategies , and Aggro Control.<br>Basically feel free to post , what type of people you look for in what type of groups,<br>and what you do to maintain aggro control on/off yourself, such as when you finally decided to cast a spell, what spell it is, and what the situations are.  Also feel free to post any general aggro control suggestions that other classes may find useful as well. <br><br>Dytren Lang<br>Sacrosanct Legion<br>&nbsp;<br>Dytren Lang<br>Sacrosanct Legion<br>The Rathe</td></tr>
